        "description": "<p>It lets your user login on to your website simply with their mobile number. No more password or email required.</p>\n<h3>Features</h3>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Passwordless login with SMS/OTP</strong></li>\n<li>Compatible with All Themes and Plugins</li>\n<li><strong>Fast and Secure</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Uses React :</strong> Lightening fast experience for users.</li>\n<li><strong>Responsive :</strong> Works seamlessly for all devices</li>\n<li><strong>Translation Ready:</strong> Compatible with WPML and RTL</li>\n<li>Non Developer Friendly</li>\n<li>Free Updates</li>\n<li><strong>Free Single International Country:</strong> Use it in your country.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><a href=\"https://orionhive.com/sms-login-static/screenshot-4.png\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Features</a></p>\n<h3>SMS Gateways Supported</h3>\n<p>It supports 6 SMS Gateways</p>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"https://youtu.be/kepFz_P05rM\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Twilio</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://youtu.be/7pCO9TMOVUI\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Nexmo</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://youtu.be/Gml5LR-437c\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">ClickSend</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://youtu.be/e-moO1AYg8Q\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">MSG91</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://youtu.be/cu2HjXy3ap4\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Clickatell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://youtu.be/w9Rbu6rhIho\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">RingCaptcha</a></li>\n</ol>\n<h3>Demo Video</h3>\n<p>Please check the demo videos</p>\n<p>[2019-06-23] Plugin Demo.</p>\n<span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/_iiigGOzwmQ?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span>\n<h3>Plugin Features &amp; Tutorials Video</h3>\n<p>[2019-06-30] Features:</p>\n<span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/cu2HjXy3ap4?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span>\n<p>[2019-06-30] Nexmo API Tutorial:</p>\n<span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/7pCO9TMOVUI?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span>\n<p>[2019-06-30] Twilio API Tutorial:</p>\n<span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/kepFz_P05rM?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span>\n<p>[2019-06-30] ClickSend API Tutorial:</p>\n<span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Gml5LR-437c?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span>\n<p>[2019-06-30] MSG91 API Tutorial:</p>\n<span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/e-moO1AYg8Q?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span>\n<p>[2019-06-30] RingCaptcha API Tutorial:</p>\n<span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/w9Rbu6rhIho?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span>\n<h3>Chat Support</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.messenger.com/t/OrionPlugins\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Chat Support</a></p>\n<h3>Installation and Use</h3>\n<p>This section describes how to install the plugin and get it working.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Upload the plugin files to the <code>/wp-content/plugins/plugin-name</code> directory, or install the plugin through the WordPress plugins screen directly.</li>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the &#8216;Plugins&#8217; screen in WordPress</li>\n<li>Go to WordPress admin Dashboard under &#8216;Orion Login Settings&#8217; Menu and fill the required fields.</li>\n<li>Get the required API key, Secret and Sender IDs etc from one of the above mentioned SMS service providers ( as per the instructions shown in the settings page )</li>\n<li>Fill the required fields as described in the plugin&#8217;s settings page.</li>\n<li>Put the form selector class name or id on the plugin settings page and the plugin will automatically create a &#8216;Login with SMS&#8217; button in your login form.</li>\n<li>When the user clicks on the &#8216;Login with SMS&#8217; button a new form will pop up, where user can enter the his phone number that he gave at the time of registration.</li>\n<li>User can receive the verification code on the registered mobile number. If he verifies the code correctly then he will be logged in and directed to home page.</li>\n<li>Plugin loads font-awesome( open source, gpl friendly ) from cdn for admin dashboard settings. However when offline everything should work as expected, except the icons would show when you are back online.</li>\n</ol>\n",
        "faq": "\n<h4>\nIts not working.\n</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Step 1. Check if your Plugin is activated.<br />\nStep 2. Deactivate all plugins and reactivate orion-login-with-sms.<br />\nStep 3. Check if all required fields are filled in the WordPress admin Dashboard under Orion Login Settings.</p>\n</p>\n\n"
